specifications.reference: Fassa Therm Eco - Silicato di Calcio Idrato

parameters.Part Number: Fassa Therm Eco - Silicato di Calcio Idrato
parameters.Description: MINERAL WOOL SLAB thermal insulating slab, produced by spinning molten rock materials into fibres. A binding resin is then added to stabilise the structure of the material, making it possible to shape it into panels.
